remove stop word

stop_word = c("，","。",".","、","(",",",")","】","【","？","\r\n","\r\n\r\n","-","\r\n2","B","A","(1)","(2)","(3)")
data = data %>% filter(!token %in% stop_word,!is.na(token),is.na(as.numeric(token)))  %>% filter(nchar(token)>1&&stri_enc_isascii(token))

tsne 文字雲

n = 500
dtm = dtm[,order(-col_sums(dtm))]
tsne = dtm[, 1:n] %>% as.data.frame.matrix %>% 
  scale %>% t %>% Rtsne(
    check_duplicates = FALSE, theta=0.0, max_iter=3200)
Y = tsne$Y              # tSNE coordinates
d = dist(Y)             # distance matrix
hc = hclust(d)          # hi-clustering
K = 50                 # number of clusters 
g = cutree(hc,K)        # cut into K clusters
table(g) %>% as.vector %>% sort         # sizes of clusters

keyword

fileName <- "query_web/dict/keyword.txt"
txt <- file(fileName,open="r")
lines <-readLines(txt)

keywords <- gsub("\\S+\t", "", lines)

keyword freq

data %>% filter(token %in% keywords)%>% group_by(token)%>%summarise(count = n()) %>% arrange(desc(count)) %>% head(20) %>%
